  "body": "<p>The <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/stamping\">Silhouette Stamping Kit</a> is one of the products I was most excited about seeing in action at CHA Create N Connect in Vegas. Doesn't every designer/creative being/person dream of creating their very own stamps?</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556797792-9YF4QS0AK25KB654MULZ/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556812805-2RD2DD55OYA4O4B7D4CQ/4b-IMG_4731.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>There's a bit of a learning curve, and it would have helped if I could have located a new blade in my piles of stuff that got moved. I think that would have made all the difference. And perhaps it's time I upgrade from the SD to the Cameo® or Portrait®, once I organize my studio. For now, I am working on the dining room table (which forces me to clean up after every single project).</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4c-IMG_4738-400x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556840181-HOCHR2YB7FPHJLIDKUV3/4c-IMG_4738-400x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"4d-IMG_4741-400x600.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556840075-QPMWTWAF87JXSA9YRD2G/4d-IMG_4741-400x600.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Confession:</em>I decided after cutting out the silhouette of the US that I wanted a heart. So I simply cut a small scrap with scissors. The material is really quite fun and if you're up for it, you can use a craft knife and mat to create shapes without the machine.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"4e-IMG_4747.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556875776-UUM3OHFUUMFXKL5ZNCC1/4e-IMG_4747.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"4f-IMG_4748.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556875628-NF0X7HUH39BJGNDDVRMA/4f-IMG_4748.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=wet%20cement&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2D41272%2FHero%2DArts%2D2012%2Dstamps%2FDetail\">Hero Arts Shadow Ink in Wet Cement</a> left an interesting impression, that I actually love the look of (and matches my table). The black ink comes in the starter kit. I wrote the love with an American Crafts .03 Precision Pen under the <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/jillibean-soup/131370-whipped-white-alphabean-cardstock-stickers/\">white alphabean stickers</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599556903543-UJOCCV4YO2HV5PJ72M1B/4g-blogger-promo-sept-2013.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/stamping\">Silhouette</a> and use the promo code: TANGERINE through September 13 to get any of these: (1) <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/stamping\">Silhouette PORTRAIT® / stamping starter kit bundle</a> $129.99 (2) <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/stamping\">Silhouette CAMEO® / stamping starter kit bundle</a> $269.99 (3) <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/stamping\">Stamping Starter Kit</a> $23.99</p><p>Happy stamping!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}